&lt;Southern Air Transport> said it suedWPLG-Channel 10 of Miami for compensatory and punitive damagesin excess of 50 mln dlrs for false and defamatory statementsmade by the television station in a series of broadcasts lastmonth.    The complaint alleges that the broadcast contained numerousfalse statements which the stations knew were untrue.    Officials of either company were unavailable for comment. Reuter&#3;